title: Dearborn Heights - *MOVE-IN SPECIAL! 1 Bedroom 1 Bath Available Now !
posting_body: ['Come see the beautiful, spacious, 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom unit at Park Forest Apartments.', 'This unit features a large fully equipped kitchen, hardwood floors, new carpet in the bedroom, spacious closets in the bedroom, and a large walk-in closet in the foyer.', 'Amenities include:', '•\tAppliances – Gas Stove, Refrigerator & Dishwasher', '•\tHardwood Floors & New Carpet in Bedroom', '•\tControlled Gates Access', '•\tSwimming Pool & Picnic Area', '•\tLaundry Facility in Each Building', '•\tResident Business Center', '•\tCovered Parking Available', 'Available Now!!', '$945 Rent/ $945 Security Deposit', 'For more information or to schedule an appointment for a showing, please call our office at', 'show contact info', '.', 'Also enjoy features such as online rent payment, online maintenance requests, and online applications.', 'Thank you for your interest.', 'Sorry, No Pets.', 'Cities close by Redford, Dearborn, Allen Park, Westland, Taylor, Wayne, Melvindale']
